<HL>
   Best Buy Co.'s Sales Increase
</HL>
<DATE>
06/07/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A9
</SO>
<CO>
   BBY
</CO>
<LP>
   MINNEAPOLIS -- Best Buy Co., a retailer, said its May
sales rose 25% to $40 million from $32 million a year
earlier. Sales in the company's first quarter ended last
Saturday rose 21% to $127 million from $105 million a year
earlier.
